                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17981205-20-defend343 t17981205-20-punish104"></join>
               Confined two years in the House of Correction
            </rs>, and <rs id="t17981205-20-punish105" type="punishmentDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17981205-20-punish105" type="punishmentCategory" value="miscPunish"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17981205-20-punish105" type="punishmentSubcategory" value="fine"></interp>
                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t17981205-20-defend343 t17981205-20-punish105"></join>
               fined 1s.
            </rs>
               </p>
               <p>Tried by the second Middlesex Jury, before Mr. RECORDER.</p>
